My deb packages rules and updating scripts for Debian and Ubuntu

Related links:
	http://qa.debian.org/developer.php?login=tehnick-8%40mail.ru
	http://mentors.debian.net/packages/uploader/tehnick-8%40mail.ru
	https://launchpad.net/~tehnick/+related-software
	http://tehnick-8.narod.ru/

Notes:
	git clone git://github.com/tehnick/deb_packages.git
	git submodule init
	git submodule update

Other commands:
	git status && git submodule foreach 'git status'
	git submodule foreach 'git checkout master && git pull --all'
	git submodule foreach 'git checkout master && git push'
